name: YOU'RE SO MONEY BABY | PRESSED POWDER PALETTE
description: The Kylie Cosmetics limited edition You're So Money Birthday Collection palette is your secret weapon to create the perfect Kylie look. Each palette comes with 9 metallics and 7 matte pressed powder pigments that can be used together to recreate Kylie’s favorite birthday looks or customize your own.

name: FACE PRIMER | BIRTHDAY 2019
description: NEW lightweight hydrating primer, refreshes skin and creates a smooth canvas for makeup application. Instantly brightens and evens out the skin and can be worn alone or with the Kylie Skin Face Moisturizer for added hydration. Increases wear of foundation and it is suitable for all skin types.

name: FACE SPRAY | SETTING SPRAY
description: The Kylie Cosmetics face spray is a weightless setting spray that is formulated to lock in makeup all day and night.

name: BIRTHDAY LOOSE ILLUMINATING POWDER
description: NEW Radiant version of our best-selling Setting Powders. It is a weightless, ultra-fine powder that blends seamlessly into skin without looking cakey or adding texture. Micro shimmers add a subtle radiance and luminosity for a healthy, luminous finish.

name: 22 CARATS | JELLY KYLIGHTER
description: High-shine Jelly Kylighter is a water-based gel cream infused with Vitamin E and concentrated blend of illuminating pearls. The lightweight, refreshing formula glides onto the skin and instantly brightens with an illuminating finish.

name: BIRTHDAY PRESSED BODY GLOW
description: NEW Ultra-creamy, pressed powder formula blends seamlessly and melts into skin for an all over, radiant glow. Multi-dimensional pearls add shine and provide a warm, luminous sheen.

name: ULTIMATE GLOW BIRTHDAY BUNDLE
description:
1 x Birthday Pressed Body Glow 
 1 x Face Primer 
 1 x Family is Gold Jelly Kylighter 
 1 x Money Ain't Everything Shimmer Glaze 
 1 x Birthday Loose Illuminating Powder

name: MAMA BOSS | MATTE LIPSTICK
description: The Kylie Cosmetics Matte Lipstick is a smooth and creamy formula that provides full coverage for an ultra-pigmented lip. The hydrating matte lipstick glides onto the lips for a comfortable matte finish. Wear alone or pair with your favorite gloss for a high shine finish.

name: MONEY ROLL MATTE LIPSTICK BUNDLE
description:
